  "term": "def:function-decreasing",
  "kind": "Definition",
  "title": "Decreasing Function",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $A\\subseteq\\mathbb{R}$ and let $f:A\\to\\mathbb{R}$. The function\n$f$ is decreasing on $A$ if\n\\[\n x_1<x_2\\;\\Longrightarrow\\;f(x_1)\\geq f(x_2)\n \\qquad (x_1,x_2\\in A).\n\\]",
